OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will be dry in the
OL,6,Feast, some hazy sunshine. Cloud and
OL,7,Frain in the west will gradually spread
OL,8,Facross all parts through the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Mild across the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy with rain through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight but some drier
OL,13,Fweather spreading from the west
OL,14,Ftowards morning. Rain turning to snow
OL,15,Fover the Southern Uplands overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FCloudy morning with rain and
OL,18,Fhill snow in the east. Dry conditions
OL,19,Fat first in the west will spread to
OL,20,Fall areas through the day with
OL,21,Fincreasing bright spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
