OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright on Saturday, clouding over
OL,7,Flater. Mostly dry with variable cloud
OL,8,Fand bright spells on Sunday and
OL,9,FMonday, but a chance of the odd spell
OL,10,Fof rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
